arguments.template:
<select [ngClass]="inputClass"
            class="form-control"
            [(ngModel)]="query"
            [formControl]="inputControl">

        <option value="">{{ column.getFilterConfig().selectText }}</option>
        <option *ngFor="let option of column.getFilterConfig().list" [value]="option.value">
          {{ option.title }}
        </option>
    </select>
